'''COVID追踪计划'''（{{lang-en|COVID Tracking Project}}）是一家专门记录[[2019冠狀病毒病美國疫情|2019冠状病毒病美国疫情]]发展的网站。其数据库记录每个[[美国州份|州]]、首都[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]和五个[[美国属地|海外属地]]的检测结果的数量，新增病例数和病例总数以及病例的种族信息。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How many coronavirus cases have been found in each U.S. state|url=https://politico.com/interactives/2020/coronavirus-testing-by-state-chart-of-new-cases/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=politico.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410191441/https://politico.com/interactives/2020/coronavirus-testing-by-state-chart-of-new-cases/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=How the COVID Tracking Project fills the public health data gap|url=https://www.cjr.org/the_profile/covid-tracking-project.php|accessdate=2021-01-13|work=Columbia Journalism Review|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410191442/https://www.cjr.org/the_profile/covid-tracking-project.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报道，网站的数据全部由志愿者手工录入，数据来源为各州卫生部门、当地新闻报道和新闻发布会。<ref>{{Cite news|title=U.S. Lags in Coronavirus Testing After Slow Response to Outbreak|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/03/17/us/coronavirus-testing-data.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-03-17|accessdate=2021-01-13|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Larry|last=Buchanan|first2=K. K. Rebecca|last2=Lai|first3=Allison|last3=McCann|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410191442/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/03/17/us/coronavirus-testing-data.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>网站的数据在[[知识共享许可协议|知识共享-署名协议]]下发布。<ref name="license">{{Cite web|title=Data License|url=https://covidtracking.com/about-data/license|accessdate=2021-01-13|work=The COVID Tracking Project|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113090632/https://covidtracking.com/about-data/license/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
2020年3月，《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》杂志记者罗宾森·梅耶和{{Le|阿列克西斯·马德里加尔|Alexis Madrigal}}由于找不到关于疫情的官方统一消息来源，自行建立了一套[[电子表格|电子表格]]来追踪2019冠状病毒病疫情的信息。几乎就在同时，分析家{{Le|杰夫·哈默巴赫|Jeff Hammerbacher}}也独立建构了类似的统计计划。两个项目于2020年3月7日合并，是为COVID追踪计划。网站上线后，邀请公众参与贡献内容，网站大部分内容都由志愿者更新。该网站还扩大了收集数据的范围，开发了应用程序接口（API）便于其他网站调用数据。<ref>{{Cite web|title=About Us|url=https://covidtracking.com/about|accessdate=2021-01-13|work=The COVID Tracking Project|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113090702/https://covidtracking.com/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年5月，[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]首次发布了官方的各州疫情病例数据，COVID追踪计划发布了官方数据与各州上报数据的对比。<ref>{{Cite web|title=State and Federal Data on COVID-19 Testing Don’t Match Up|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2020/05/cdc-publishing-covid-19-test-data/611764/|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2020-05-17|last=Madrigal|first=Robinson Meyer, Alexis C.|work=The Atlantic|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113090631/https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2020/05/cdc-publishing-covid-19-test-data/611764/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年2月1日，COVID追踪计划宣布其将于2021年3月7日最后一次更新数据，网站将在5月关闭。<ref>{{cite web |author1 = Erin Kissane |author2 = Alexis Madrigal |title = It's Time: The COVID Tracking Project Will Soon Come to an End |url = https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/covid-tracking-project-end-march-7 |website = The COVID Tracking Project |date = 2021-02-01 |access-date = 2021-02-23 |language = en-US |archive-date = 2021-05-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210524201458/https://covidtracking.com/analysis-updates/covid-tracking-project-end-march-7/ }}</ref>

